com.models

Class Parcel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.models.Parcel

  • public class Parcel
extends java.lang.Object
    Author: Jim Parcels Class: Collection of Statc Inner Class Models that our Servlets need to understand to communicate with the front-end. Use these in coordination with GSON to easily produce JSON Strings from Objects and vice versa. Most of the communication will be push, i.e. from server to client, but these are still helpful in case the client translates from server to client. For more info see DESIGNDOCS (Google Docs).
